Beef flavor cats love Savory gravy for added moisture and flavor Tender chunks deliver a tempting texture Contains essential vitamins and minerals 100% complete and balanced nutrition formulated for adult cats Part of the complete line of Purina Friskies wet and dry cat foods Checked for quality and safety Offer up more of the delicious gravy goodness your cat loves in her dish with Purina Friskies Extra Gravy With Beef In Savory Gravy Chunky wet cat food. Tender chunks of meaty deliciousness give your cat the taste and texture she craves with every bite, and the hearty helping of extra gravy provides her with a mouthwatering reason to lick her dish clean at feeding time. Let your cat delight in the savory tastes, and rest easy knowing she's getting a high-quality meal in every can. Essential vitamins and minerals help to support your adult cat's overall health and wellness, making this wet cat food a smart way to provide 100% complete and balanced nutrition formulated for adult cats. With so much yumminess packed into every bite, this Purina Friskies wet cat food lets you show your cat companion just how much you care about her health and happiness every time you reach for a can. Get your cat into the gravy groove when you serve Purina Friskies Extra Gravy With Beef In Savory Gravy Chunky wet cat food. Each bite is smothered in extra gravy for more of the taste cats love, and the tempting texture gives her something scrumptious to sink her teeth into. You can rest easy knowing she's getting the quality that comes from a trusted brand, and she can feel good about having savory goodness in her dish at mealtime. This recipe is formulated for adult cats, giving her the nutrition she needs to be her adventurous self. Packaged in a convenient single-serving can, this recipe is easy to serve whenever your cat is ready for an irresistible meal. Feed this wet cat food according to the serving instructions based on her weight, and make it a part of her regular feeding routine. For more variety at mealtime, let your cat explore our complete line of crave-worthy recipes, including Purina Friskies Indoor Delights dry cat food or Purina Friskies Cat Concoctions wet cat foods, and let her select the flavors and textures she loves the best.

Your cat is the center of your world, and you want to make sure she gets nothing but the best in her dish. That's why we strive to make quality the top priority in every wet and dry cat food and treat we produce. Our cat food undergoes rigorous quality and safety tests to give you added peace of mind every time you reach for a can. We are constantly working to elevate our ability to track and monitor our ingredients throughout the manufacturing process. We formulate our recipes to meet or exceed federal and state requirements for pet food. The result is delicious, nutritious and safe meals you can feel proud to serve to your feline friend. Give your cat a delectable reason to prance to her dish when you offer up Purina Friskies Extra Gravy With Beef In Savory Gravy Chunky wet cat food at mealtime.

Any other trademarks are property of their respective owners. 100% complete and balanced nutrition for kittens and adult cats Delicious slow-cooked cuts of tuna Gravy enhances seafood and cheddar flavor Essential vitamins and minerals help maintain a healthy body condition Small, delicate bites  are easy for kittens and adults to eat Rigorously tested for quality and safety Made by a brand with more than 80 years of experience in producing top-quality pet food Give your cat a delightful gourmet meal with Purina Fancy Feast Delights Grilled Tuna & Cheddar Cheese Feast in Gravy cat food. The 3-ounce can contains a medley of flavors designed to stimulate your cat's senses while also providing a healthy meal that delivers 100% complete and balanced nutrition. Both kittens and adult cats can enjoy the classic grilled tuna flavor, and cheddar cheese adds a taste of dairy that will have your cat anticipating her next meal. Fancy Feast is true gourmet cat food featuring tender morsels of slow-cooked tuna that your cat is sure to love. Not only that, Purina wet cat food is backed by more than 80 years of experience providing pet food that is both nutritious and delicious. Our incredibly high standards for safety and quality ensure that each meal you give your cat is the luxury dining experience she deserves. Feel good about the meal you feed your cat by providing her with Purina Fancy Feast Delights Grilled Tuna & Cheddar Cheese Feast in Gravy cat food. This wet cat food has flavors she loves, including cheddar cheese to provide a taste of dairy cats crave and delicious, slow-cooked cuts of tuna. This gourmet cat food is made for both kittens and adult cats, so the 100% complete and balanced nutrition provided in each 3-ounce can means that your cat isn't just getting a tasty meal, but an entree that helps sustain her energy and health for years of playtime . It's a taste your cat can trust, with real fish broth and tuna as the first ingredients. The seafood in this cat food is more than simply a delectable mealtime flavor. It's also sustainably sourced, so you're taking care of both the environment and your favorite feline with every serving. Our rigorous standards for gourmet-quality food mean that any of our Delights with Cheddar meals are delicious when paired together or enjoyed alone. Give your cat more seafood to savor when you serve her our Grilled Whitefish & Cheddar Cheese Feast in Gravy.

Purina has more than 80 years of innovative experience in creating quality pet food. We are committed to making sure every single serving you give your cat meets or exceeds industry standards. To further ensure your peace of mind, our food is crafted in facilities that receive hourly checks for safety and quality assurance. We not only ensure your cat a lifetime of delicious meals, but our dedication to the environment means we are committed to responsibly sourcing our food's ingredients. Our cans are fully recyclable, and we're working to reduce our water consumption at every stage of production to minimize our environmental impact.
